M20.354 15.354A9 9 0 018.646 3.646 9.003 9.003 0 0012 21a9.003 9.003 0 008.354-5.646z\"></path></svg></button><a class=\"hidden rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition sm:block text-brand-charcoal hover:bg-white\" href=\"/login\">Ingia</a><a class=\"rounded-lg bg-brand-green px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-brand-green-dark hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-green/25\" href=\"/register\">Jisajili Bure</a></div></div></nav><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden px-6 pb-16 pt-28 md:px-12 lg:px-24 lg:pb-24 lg:pt-36\"><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute -right-40 -top-40 h-[500px] w-[500px] rounded-full blur-[120px] bg-brand-green/10\"></div><div class=\"absolute -left-40 bottom-0 h-[400px] w-[400px] rounded-full blur-[120px] bg-brand-orange/10\"></div></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center gap-16 lg:flex-row lg:justify-between\"><div class=\"max-w-xl text-center lg:text-left\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px);transition:opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold bg-brand-green/10 text-brand-green\"><span class=\"relative flex h-2 w-2\"><span class=\"absolute inline-flex h-full w-full animate-ping rounded-full bg-brand-green opacity-75\"></span><span class=\"relative inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-green\"></span></span>Kwa Migahawa ya Tanzania</div><h1 class=\"mt-6 text-4xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl\">Simamia Mgahawa Wako<br/><span class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-green to-brand-green-light bg-clip-text text-transparent\">Kutoka Simu</span></h1><p class=\"mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600\">POS, Stoku, Gharama, na Faida yako halisi — yote katika mfumo mmoja rahisi. Hakuna karatasi, hakuna Excel, hakuna kubahatisha.</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400\">Manage your restaurant from your phone. Sales, stock, expenses, and real profit — all in one system.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center lg:justify-start\"><a class=\"group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-brand-green px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-brand-green/25 transition-all hover:bg-brand-green-dark hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-brand-green/30\" href=\"/register\"><span>Anza Bure — Siku 14</span><svg class=\"h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6\"></path></svg></a><a class=\"rounded-xl border-2 px-8 py-4 text-center text-base font-semibold transition-all border-brand-green/20 text-brand-green hover:border-brand-green/40 hover:bg-brand-green/5\" href=\"#features\">Angalia Zaidi</a></div><p class=\"mt-5 text-xs text-gray-400\">Hakuna kadi ya benki · Jisajili kwa namba ya simu · M-Pesa, Tigo, Airtel, Halo</p></div><div class=\"relative flex-shrink-0\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px);transition:opacity 1s ease 0.3s, transform 1s ease 0.3s\"><div class=\"relative mx-auto h-[580px] w-[280px] rounded-[40px] border-4 p-2 shadow-2xl border-brand-charcoal bg-white\"><div class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 z-10 h-6 w-24 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-b-xl bg-brand-charcoal\"></div><div class=\"h-full overflow-hidden rounded-[32px] bg-brand-cream\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between bg-brand-green-dark px-4 pb-1 pt-8\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-white/70\">FoodOS</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-white/70\">09:41</span></div><div class=\"bg-brand-green px-4 pb-4 pt-2\"><p class=\"text-[10px] text-white/70\">Habari, Mama Salma</p><p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-white\">Leo - Dashboard</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 p-3\"><div class=\"rounded-xl p-3 shadow-sm bg-white\"><p class=\"text-[9px] text-gray-500\">Mapato</p><p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-brand-green\">TZS 450K</p><p class=\"text-[8px] text-gray-400\">+12%</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl p-3 shadow-sm bg-white\"><p class=\"text-[9px] text-gray-500\">Gharama Bidhaa</p><p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-brand-orange\">TZS 180K</p><p class=\"text-[8px] text-gray-400\">40%</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl p-3 shadow-sm bg-white\"><p class=\"text-[9px] text-gray-500\">Matumizi</p><p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-gray-700\">TZS 35K</p><p class=\"text-[8px] text-gray-400\">Gesi, Ufungaji</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl p-3 shadow-sm bg-white\"><p class=\"text-[9px] text-gray-500\">Faida Halisi</p><p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-brand-green\">TZS 235K</p><p class=\"text-[8px] text-gray-400\">52% margin</p></div></div><div class=\"mx-3 rounded-xl p-3 shadow-sm bg-white\"><p class=\"text-[9px] font-medium text-gray-500\">Mauzo - Wiki Hii</p><div class=\"mt-2 flex items-end gap-1.5\"><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col items-center gap-1\"><div class=\"w-full rounded-t\" style=\"height:32.5px;background-color:#2D7A3A;opacity:0.6\"></div><span class=\"text-[7px] text-gray-400\">Ju</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col items-center gap-1\"><div class=\"w-full rounded-t\" style=\"height:22.5px;background-color:#2D7A3A;opacity:0.65\"></div><span class=\"text-[7px] text-gray-400\">Ju</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col items-center gap-1\"><div class=\"w-full rounded-t\" style=\"height:40px;background-color:#2D7A3A;opacity:0.7\"></div><span class=\"text-[7px] text-gray-400\">Al</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col items-center gap-1\"><div class=\"w-full rounded-t\" style=\"height:27.5px;background-color:#2D7A3A;opacity:0.75\"></div><span class=\"text-[7px] text-gray-400\">Al</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col items-center gap-1\"><div class=\"w-full rounded-t\" style=\"height:45px;background-color:#2D7A3A;opacity:0.8\"></div><span class=\"text-[7px] text-gray-400\">Ij</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col items-center gap-1\"><div class=\"w-full rounded-t\" style=\"height:35px;background-color:#2D7A3A;opacity:0.85\"></div><span class=\"text-[7px] text-gray-400\">Ju</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col items-center gap-1\"><div class=\"w-full rounded-t\" style=\"height:42.5px;background-color:#E8712B;opacity:1\"></div><span class=\"text-[7px] text-gray-400\">Leo</span></div></div></div><div class=\"mx-3 mt-2 rounded-lg bg-red-500/10 p-2\"><p class=\"text-[9px] font-medium text-red-500\">Stoku Chini: Mchele 3kg, Nyama 2kg</p></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-2 left-2 right-2 flex items-center justify-around rounded-2xl py-2 shadow-md bg-white\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5\"><div class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-brand-green\"></div><span class=\"text-[7px] font-bold text-brand-green\">Dashboard</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5\"><div class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-gray-200\"></div><span class=\"text-[7px] text-gray-400\">POS</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5\"><div class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-gray-200\"></div><span class=\"text-[7px] text-gray-400\">Stoku</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5\"><div class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-gray-200\"></div><span class=\"text-[7px] text-gray-400\">Ripoti</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute -left-6 top-16 rounded-xl px-3 py-2 shadow-lg bg-white\"><p class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-brand-green\">M-Pesa</p><p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-brand-charcoal\">Malipo Papo</p></div><div class=\"absolute -right-6 top-40 rounded-xl px-3 py-2 shadow-lg bg-white\"><p class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-brand-orange\">Idhini</p><p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-brand-charcoal\">2 Zinasubiri</p></div><div class=\"absolute -left-2 bottom-24 rounded-xl px-3 py-2 shadow-lg bg-white\"><p class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-green-500\">Offline</p><p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-brand-charcoal\">Inafanya Kazi</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"features\" class=\"px-6 py-20 md:px-12 lg:px-24 bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease 0s, transform 0.7s ease 0s\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-4xl\">Kila Kitu Unahitaji, Pahali Pamoja</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-3 max-w-lg text-sm text-gray-500\">Everything you need to run your restaurant — in one place</p></div><div class=\"mt-14 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease 0s, transform 0.7s ease 0s\"><div class=\"group h-full rounded-2xl border p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg border-gray-100 bg-brand-cream hover:border-brand-green/20 hover:shadow-brand-green/10\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-green/10\"><svg class=\"h-6 w-6 text-brand-green\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 14l6-6m-5.5.5h.01m4.99 5h.01M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16l3.5-2 3.5 2 3.5-2 3.5 2z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold\">POS - Pata Oda</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600\">Menu grid, tap to order, malipo ya M-Pesa, Tigo, Cash — haraka na rahisi</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease 0.1s, transform 0.7s ease 0.1s\"><div class=\"group h-full rounded-2xl border p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg border-gray-100 bg-brand-cream hover:border-brand-green/20 hover:shadow-brand-green/10\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-green/10\"><svg class=\"h-6 w-6 text-brand-green\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold\">Stoku - Fuatilia Bidhaa</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600\">Ingiza bidhaa, toa, hariri — yote chini ya idhini ya mkurugenzi</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease 0.2s, transform 0.7s ease 0.2s\"><div class=\"group h-full rounded-2xl border p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg border-gray-100 bg-brand-cream hover:border-brand-green/20 hover:shadow-brand-green/10\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-green/10\"><svg class=\"h-6 w-6 text-brand-green\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold\">Faida Halisi</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600\">Mapato - Gharama Bidhaa - Matumizi = Faida yako halisi kwa wakati halisi</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease 0.30000000000000004s, transform 0.7s ease 0.30000000000000004s\"><div class=\"group h-full rounded-2xl border p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg border-gray-100 bg-brand-cream hover:border-brand-green/20 hover:shadow-brand-green/10\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-green/10\"><svg class=\"h-6 w-6 text-brand-green\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M3 3v18h18M9 17V9m4 8V5m4 12v-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold\">Ripoti za Kila Siku</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600\">Mauzo, gharama, faida — kila siku, wiki, mwezi kwenye simu yako</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease 0.4s, transform 0.7s ease 0.4s\"><div class=\"group h-full rounded-2xl border p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg border-gray-100 bg-brand-cream hover:border-brand-green/20 hover:shadow-brand-green/10\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-green/10\"><svg class=\"h-6 w-6 text-brand-green\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold\">Mfumo wa Idhini</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600\">Kila badiliko la stoku linahitaji kibali — hakuna wizi</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease 0.5s, transform 0.7s ease 0.5s\"><div class=\"group h-full rounded-2xl border p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg border-gray-100 bg-brand-cream hover:border-brand-green/20 hover:shadow-brand-green/10\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-green/10\"><svg class=\"h-6 w-6 text-brand-green\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M8.111 16.404a5.5 5.5 0 017.778 0M12 20h.01m-7.08-7.071c3.904-3.905 10.236-3.905 14.14 0M1.394 9.393c5.857-5.858 15.355-5.858 21.213 0\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold\">Inafanya Kazi Offline</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600\">Hata wakati wa kukatika umeme — mfumo unafanya kazi</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"px-6 py-20 md:px-12 lg:px-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease 0s, transform 0.7s ease 0s\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-4xl\">Watu 3, Mfumo 1</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-3 max-w-lg text-sm text-gray-500\">3 people, 1 system — replaces 6-7 staff members</p></div><div class=\"mt-14 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease 0s, transform 0.7s ease 0s\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-2xl border p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg border-gray-100 bg-white shadow-md\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-brand-green/10 text-brand-green dark:bg-brand-green/20\"><div class=\"h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-brand-green\"></div></div><h3 class=\"mt-5 text-lg font-bold\">Mkurugenzi</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">Owner</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600\">Angalia faida, thibitisha stoku, simamia kutoka nyumbani</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease 0.15s, transform 0.7s ease 0.15s\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-2xl border p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg border-gray-100 bg-white shadow-md\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-brand-orange/10 text-brand-orange dark:bg-brand-orange/20\"><div class=\"h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-brand-orange\"></div></div><h3 class=\"mt-5 text-lg font-bold\">Msimamizi Stoku</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">Stock Manager</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600\">Ingiza bidhaa, toa, hariri — yote yanahitaji idhini</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease 0.3s, transform 0.7s ease 0.3s\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-2xl border p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg border-gray-100 bg-white shadow-md\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-brand-gold/10 text-brand-gold dark:bg-brand-gold/20\"><div class=\"h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-brand-gold\"></div></div><h3 class=\"mt-5 text-lg font-bold\">Karani</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">Cashier</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600\">Pata oda, pokea malipo ya M-Pesa na Cash</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"px-6 py-20 md:px-12 lg:px-24 bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease 0s, transform 0.7s ease 0s\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-4xl\">Bei Rahisi</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-3 max-w-lg text-sm text-gray-500\">Simple pricing — start free, upgrade when you grow</p></div><div class=\"mx-auto mt-14 grid max-w-3xl gap-6 md:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease 0s, transform 0.7s ease 0s\"><div class=\"relative h-full rounded-2xl border p-7 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 border-gray-200\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold\">Bure<span class=\"ml-1 text-sm font-normal text-gray-400\">(<!-- -->Free Trial<!-- -->)</span></h3><div class=\"mt-3 flex items-baseline gap-1\"><span class=\"text-sm\">TZS</span><span class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold\">0</span></div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\">Siku 14</p><ul class=\"mt-6 space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm\"><svg class=\"h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-brand-green\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"></pa